'''法國足球聯賽系統'''橫跨[[法國|法國]]及[[摩納哥|摩納哥]]的球隊，亦包含一支西班牙球隊。首兩級的[[法甲|法甲]]和[[法乙|法乙]]屬職業<ref>{{cite web | url = http://new.lfp.fr | publisher = [[Ligue_de_Football_Professionnel|Ligue de Football Professionnel]] | title = LFP, Ligue 1, L1, Ligue 2, L2 et Coupe de le Ligue. | language = fr | date =  | accessdate = 9 December 2010 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101016155121/http://new.lfp.fr/ | archive-date = 2010-10-16 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35816.shtml | publisher = [[法國足球總會|法國足球總會]] | title = Ligue 1 | language = fr | date =  | accessdate = 9 December 2010 | archive-date = 2013-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130127171805/http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35816.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35817.shtml | publisher = [[法國足球總會|法國足球總會]] | title = Ligue 2 | language = fr | date =  | accessdate = 9 December 2010 | archive-date = 2013-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130127171845/http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35817.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。而第三級的[[法丙|法丙]]屬半職業<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35818.shtml | publisher = [[法國足球總會|法國足球總會]] | title = Championnat National | language = fr | date =  | accessdate = 9 December 2010 | archive-date = 2013-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130127171647/http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35818.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。第四、五級的全國業餘聯賽，及他們以下的地區聯賽均全屬業餘<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35820.shtml | publisher = [[法國足球總會|法國足球總會]] | title = 法國業餘聯賽 | language = fr | date =  | accessdate = 9 December 2010 | archive-date = 2013-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130127171529/http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35820.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35821.shtml | publisher = [[法國足球總會|法國足球總會]] | title = 法國業餘聯賽 2 | language = fr | date =  | accessdate = 9 December 2010 | archive-date = 2013-01-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130127171818/http://www.fff.fr/presentationfff/liens/35821.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>，一般而言，在每個組別的聯賽之間設有[[升降班制度|升降班制度]]。

